name: HAMILTON CHAMPIONS TM Enhanced U.S. Dividend ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of Fund is to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses, a multiple of the performance of a U.S. equity dividend index. Specifically, SWIN currently seeks to replicate a 1.25 times multiple of the Solactive United States Dividend Elite Champions Index (or any successor thereto).
